Package: featuretablefilter
Type: Package
Title: Feature Table Filtering for Microbiome Data
Version: 0.99.0
Author: Vojtech Barton [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Vojtech Barton <vojtech.barton@gmail.com>
Authors@R: person("Vojtech", "Barton", email = "vojtech.barton@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for filtering microbiome feature tables based on
    coverage, abundance, and network connectivity criteria. The package supports
    native handling of 'phyloseq' and 'TreeSummarizedExperiment' objects, providing
    comprehensive quality control metrics and visualizations for filtering decisions.
    It is intended for microbiome researchers who need reproducible, class-preserving
    filtering workflows with built-in diagnostics and interactive exploration.
